item.title: Jio True 5G services now available in Andhra Pradesh
item.description: Jio True 5G services now available in Andhra Pradesh The 5G services were launched in Tirumala, Visakhapatnam, Vijayawada, and Guntur districts.

item.title: AP lagging behind in IT, says BJP MP
item.description: AP lagging behind in IT, says BJP MP Talking to reporters on Sunday, he pointed out that five lakh employees were working from home and several lakhs had gone to Bangalore for IT jobs.
